EU Calls Upon Slovak Parties to Approve Bailout Fund Agreement

-- B y   P a t r i c k   H e n r y
-- 
2011-10-12T10:26:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/eu-calls-upon-slovak-parties-to-approve-bailout-fund-agreement.html
The European Union called on
Slovakia to approve enhancements to the euro area’s temporary
bailout fund, the European Financial Stability Facility.  “We call on all parties in the Slovak parliament” to rise
above party positions and secure agreement on the EFSF as soon
as possible, European Commission spokeswoman Pia Ahrenkilde-
Hansen told reporters in Brussels today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Patrick Henry  at 
 phenry8@bloomberg.net  